{"tid":1077750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華富真係愈來愈邪","createTime":"2019-03-25T21:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T11:42:23.000Z","uid":241175,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4f367d088fa51bd72ef2dbad965e87e9df08a36c","tid":1077750,"uid":241175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T21:04:43.000Z","msg":"話說琴日又多一單自殺案<br />\n華富邨公園男子上吊當場證實死亡<br />\n<br />\n首先 rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先係上年12月一單雙屍案一單棄屍案<br />\n之後今年又多2單自殺案<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為其中一個居民真係睇到好心寒<br />\n<br />\n我細個比人話係陰陽眼<br />\n又咩靈異體質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上小學時比人用亂葬岡e樣野嚇過<br />\n老實講我都成日疑心疑鬼 feel到有野跟住<br />\n我一直都諗 心理作用嚟姐<br />\n不過都係停唔到果種感覺<br />\n<br />\n上星期嘅事已經令到我晚晚冇覺好瞓<br />\n我唔知點先可以令到我安心<br />\n各位巴打絲打講嘅我都有試做過<br />\n但都冇咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好怕我會變成下一個"},{"pid":"6a5423cc63eb93856dd34625fcbbbed5575bd213","tid":1077750,"uid":52819,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T21:15:09.000Z","msg":"唔信就係係唔信<br />\n<br />\n唔信既放你係墳場一晚都無事<br />\n<br />\n信既你就嚇到痴左線咁出返黎<br />\n<br />\n自己調整下心態 正面啲就無事"},{"pid":"ccac61e5b37917f58ab9fa97229b4d288e3b577c","tid":1077750,"uid":241175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a5423cc63eb93856dd34625fcbbbed5575bd213","tid":1077750,"uid":52819,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T21:15:09.000Z","msg":"唔信就係係唔信<br />\n<br />\n唔信既放你係墳場一晚都無事<br />\n<br />\n信既你就嚇到痴左線咁出返黎<br />\n<br />\n自己調整下心態 正面啲就無事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T21:17:27.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<br />\n我都努力緊嘗試正面d<br />\n多d約朋友 唔好自己一個毒<br />\n希望可以擺脫到啦"},{"pid":"0e2a8da7eaf5543a34e0378664e1079a7cdb58c9","tid":1077750,"uid":241175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T21:20:31.000Z","msg":"不過咁岩睇新聞見到又一位伯伯自尋短見<br />\n仲要又係華富<br />\n真係好心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba61dae04d89c586620e53405e8c03d1073bd353","tid":1077750,"uid":106165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e2a8da7eaf5543a34e0378664e1079a7cdb58c9","tid":1077750,"uid":241175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T21:20:31.000Z","msg":"不過咁岩睇新聞見到又一位伯伯自尋短見<br />\n仲要又係華富<br />\n真係好心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T21:22:05.000Z","msg":"你特別留意華富姐"},{"pid":"8f1b9773c2d21f29436883a36320145895aaf3ad","tid":1077750,"uid":241175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba61dae04d89c586620e53405e8c03d1073bd353","tid":1077750,"uid":106165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e2a8da7eaf5543a34e0378664e1079a7cdb58c9","tid":1077750,"uid":241175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T21:20:31.000Z","msg":"不過咁岩睇新聞見到又一位伯伯自尋短見<br />\n仲要又係華富<br />\n真係好心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T21:22:05.000Z","msg":"你特別留意華富姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T21:24:26.000Z","msg":"話曬自己住左係到10幾年（仲住緊<br />\n半年連續出幾單命案真係幾恐怖下"},{"pid":"0ca14fa033a35b67202069ee9479ab43341191e7","tid":1077750,"uid":187109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T21:28:30.000Z","msg":"真係